	<p style="font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0 10px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold">
What's West Coast Swing?
	</p>
	<p style="font-size: 15px; margin: 0 auto 0; max-width: 533px;">
West Coast Swing is a contemporary partnered dance with roots in Lindy Hop
(swing dancing) but a style all its own. It values creativity, musicality,
improvisation, and can be danced to almost any style of music. If you've never
seen it before, check out <a href="https://youtu.be/v4fRV0aG3lc">this video
showing some of the best of the best</a>!
	</p>
